        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="py-24 bg-gray-50" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4">{{ 'How SignForge Works'|trans }}</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      {{ 'A simple, structured process to help you generate business documents effortlessly.'|trans }}
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 text-left">
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-md rounded-xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full text-xl font-bold mb-6">1</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">{{ 'Set Up Your Company'|trans }}</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500">{{ "Once you're logged in, start by creating your company profile. Upload your logo and business information — it will be used automatically in all documents."|trans }}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-md rounded-xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full text-xl font-bold mb-6">2</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">{{ 'Add Your First Client'|trans }}</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500">{{ 'Create at least one client profile. Add their company name, contact details, and billing information. You can reuse them for all future documents.'|trans }}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-md rounded-xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full text-xl font-bold mb-6">3</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">{{ 'Generate & Download'|trans }}</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500">{{ 'Select the document type (invoice, quote, contract…), fill in the dynamic form, and download your PDF instantly — ready to send or archive.'|trans }}</p>
      </div>
